permitting an optional \fI\)Load Selection\fR parameter to be included in the
ASP Inactive (ASPIA) and ASP Inactive Ack (ASPIA ACK) message.  The \fI\)Load
Selection\fR parameter is used to indicate for which traffic in the \fI\)Load
Group\fR the concerned Application Server is becoming inactive.
